14 SECTION 176, IS AMENDED TO READ AS FOLLOWS
15 [EFFECTIVE JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 132. "Noneconomic damages", for
16 purposes of IC 34-30-29.2 and IC 34-51-1-4, has the meaning set forth
17 in IC 34-30-29.2-2.
